(firstQuint)The Effect of Preoperative Pain on POCD in Elderly Patients.

 Postoperative cognitive dysfunction (POCD) occurs mainly in aged patients.

 The mechanism of POCD is not clear yet and no effective therapy method .

The purpose of this study is to investigate the effects of preoperative pain on POCD in elder patients.

